{
  "stem": "1502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Also, the beginning was all the Jewish businesses-- as I talk, I-- I remind myself-- all Jewish businesses, even before they had to liquidate, they had to put out a sign, [GERMAN], Jewish enterprise.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And-- and as-- as time went on, the laws became stricter and stricter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed to be doctors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Aryan doctors-- Aryan, with the Aryan race, means non-Jewish doctors-- were not allowed to treat Jewish patients.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Hospitals were not allowed to take in Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Jews should have their own hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "The surgeons, not allowed to operate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Jewish surgeons, not allowed to operate on Aryans, Aryans, not on Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But these were all laws that we could live with, because we had Jewish doctors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I got sick during the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I had a very bad case of measles, and I had a very high temperature.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I had two doctors, daily.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And-- and both Belgian and non-- non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They did not care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They did not care what the-- about the German laws.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They did treat Jewish patients.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And they did admit Jews into the hospitals, despite all the laws, and-- which was a nice gesture, because they could have been sent to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I mean, you know, there was no-- it was not a-- a situation, like you needed a hearing for anything, or you could appeal.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They grabbed people to send them to concentration camps, or they shot them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "That's the-- that was the-- that was the rule.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And the restrictions became-- became more difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "The-- we could not make a living.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We could not work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We could not do business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "They cut off the means from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Then came the restriction of walking in the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
